data.description: Welcome to Kings Isle, a prestigious guard gated 55+ active community located in beautiful St. Lucie West, FL. This home features charming 2bdrm 2 bth plus den that can be 3rd bdrm. Vaulted ceilings add a touch of elegance, enclosed sunroom too. Not only does this home with new AC, new washer/dryer and new refrigerator. Move in ready. Some furniture negotiable. Enjoy the community pool, hot tub, pickleball, tennis,. gym and much more! Convenience is key, as this community is located close to variety of restaurants, shopping, I95. Whether looking for a peaceful retirement or active lifestyle, Kings Isle has it all. Seller is motivated. Don't miss out on this opportunity to live in a vibrant, welcoming community.
